    "pubYear" : 2016,
    "title" : "Age of the Mt. Ortles ice cores, the Tyrolean Iceman and glaciation of the highest summit of South Tyrol since the Northern Hemisphere Climatic Optimum",
    "journal" : "The Cryosphere",
